---
// src/components/SouthVan/SouthVanNeighbourhood.astro
---

<section class="svn">
  <div class="svn-inner">
    <div class="svn-copy">
      <span class="eyebrow eyebrow-gold">Where We Train</span>
      <h2 class="svn-title">Rooted in South Vancouver</h2>
      <p class="svn-body">
        South Vancouver is one of the most underserved parts of the city when it comes to
        high-quality football development. South Van FC exists to change that. We run training
        sessions at the parks and pitches our players grew up playing at.
      </p>
      <p class="svn-body">
        Fraserview, Killarney, Champlain Heights, Sunset, Victoria-Fraserview. These
        neighbourhoods are not a backdrop for what we do. They are the reason we exist.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="svn-detail">
      <div class="svn-card">
        <div class="sc-icon">🏟️</div>
        <div>
          <div class="sc-title">Memorial Turf — Home Field</div>
          <div class="sc-desc">Our primary home field for both Youth Academy and Men's Team training and matches. Located in South Vancouver.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="svn-card">
        <div class="sc-icon">📍</div>
        <div>
          <div class="sc-title">Fraserview &amp; Killarney</div>
          <div class="sc-desc">The South Vancouver neighbourhoods the club calls home. Our players and families come from the streets and schools right here.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="svn-card">
        <div class="sc-icon">📍</div>
        <div>
          <div class="sc-title">Champlain Heights &amp; Sunset</div>
          <div class="sc-desc">Additional South Van neighbourhoods represented in our squads, with supplementary sessions at local parks when needed.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .svn {
    background: var(--navy-dark);
    padding: 96px 80px;
  }

  .svn-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .svn-title {
    font-family: "Inter Variable", sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(32px, 3.5vw, 48px);
    line-height: 1.08;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: #fff;
    margin: 12px 0 24px;
  }

  .svn-body {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    max-width: 480px;
  }

  .svn-detail {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .svn-card {
    display: flex;
    gap: 18px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
    padding: 24px 28px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .svn-card:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
  }

  .sc-icon {
    font-size: 22px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .sc-title {
    font-family: "Inter Variable", sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    letter-spacing: 0.3px;
  }

  .sc-desc {
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
  }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .svn {
      padding: 64px 28px;
    }
    .svn-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 48px;
    }
    .svn-body {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
